#### text ####
text: The day before WorldCon we finally made it to some museums!
#### location ####
text: National Leprechaun Museum of Ireland
----
lat: 53.3476109
----
lon: -6.2663478999999995
#### text ####
text: On the recommendation of a friend, we went to the Leprechaun Museum. It was a fun museum on Irish storytelling, with an immersive set of visuals. Recommended!
#### image-collection ####
images:

##### image #####
image: eJ8MsisuEF_QngQOgKQ5Z0iRQNA.jpg
-----
alt: TODO
-----
css_classes: 
-----
caption: 
