#### text ####
text: The day after WorldCon (which may have been a mistake, after late-night post-con fun) we took a tour up to the Hill of Tara and Newgrange.
#### image-collection ####
images:

##### image #####
image: ubJ0ViMuMN_8po1DTZAhNK6FKDk.jpg
-----
