#### text ####
text: We lucked into being there for the Friday market! We ate delicious crepes and browsed the stalls for souvenirs before getting back on the road.
#### text ####
text: The drive back was filled with more incomparable Irish scenery. West Cork is famous for its amazing scenery, and it did not disappoint. Everyone talks about how green and beautiful Ireland is, and I thought that surely they were exaggerating, but they were not. Ireland really is this beautiful and green, full of rolling hills decorated with castles, sheep and cows.
