#### location ####
text: The Butter Museum
----
lat: 51.9027649
----
lon: -8.4767349
#### text ####
text: Our last day was spent exploring Cork with a friend we met at WorldCon
#### text ####
text: The Butter Museum was too bizarre to pass up! It included a live demo (with audience participation!) of making butter, and then getting to eat it on delicious bread. It was amazing for a city girl like me to see it go from milk to butter in front of my eyes (and the presenter was very enthusiastic!)
#### image-collection ####
